name: Ownership Display
description: This OBJKT will display its current owners. Every time this page is loaded, the list of owners is hashed with SHA256 to derive the “current_owners_hash”. This hash is then broken up into ten hex color codes, which are used to create the unique “color_hashcode” bar. Every time the list of owners changes, the “current_owners_hash” and “color_hashcode” will also change.
